// llms.txt — helps AI tools (ChatGPT, Perplexity, Claude, etc.) understand the site
app.get('/llms.txt', (req, res) => {
  const baseUrl = process.env.BASE_URL || 'https://cutthelock.com';

  const content = `# Cut The Lock

> We buy abandoned storage units, reunite original owners with their
> irreplaceable personal belongings, and resell everything else through
> a curated online marketplace.

Important notes:
- Cut The Lock is a recovery-first business, not just a resale store
- Sentimental and personal items are returned to former tenants at no cost
- We are NOT a debt collection service
- Based in Austin / Round Rock, TX

## Services

- [Recovery Database](${baseUrl}): Submit a claim if you lost items in a storage auction
- [Marketplace](${baseUrl}): Browse curated secondhand items from recovered storage units
- [Former Tenant Options](${baseUrl}/get-your-stuff-back): Buy back your full unit or priority-pick items before they go public

### Storage Locker Buy Back
Former tenants can buy back their entire storage unit at Cut The Lock's purchase price plus a 25% fee (covers labor, transport, supplies, and overhead). This option is available before any items are sorted or listed for resale.

### Previous Owner's Priority Picking (POPP)
If a former tenant doesn't want the full unit back, they can purchase select items at resale value before anything is listed on the public marketplace. This gives previous owners first access to their belongings at fair market pricing.

## Contact

- Website: ${baseUrl}
- Email: contact@cutthelock.com
- Location: Austin / Round Rock, TX
`;

  res.type('text/plain').send(content);
});

